node.text:
It’s here!!! I couldn’t be more excited to launch this skincare capsule in collaboration with Sonya Dakar! Officially launching on Nov 9th, 2020! This kit encapsulates the products from Sonya Dakar that I attribute to the progress, clarity and overall health of my skin, all in perfect sizes to trial them for yourself (the sizes I travel with!). I hope you will love as much as I do!

PRE-SALE LINK:
https://sonyadakar.com/products/helen-owen-holiday-beauty-capsule

node.text:
In lieu of heading down to the desert today, here are some memories as told by my iPhone camera roll. Not intended to disregard the pain and suffering in the world right now, but just to look back fondly on the times we celebrated being together and alive, and to look forward to more to come.

Song is “Corners Of The Earth (feat. RY X) by ODESZA

node.text: @pvolve, my favorite, low impact, *big results* workout method. Since I discovered @pvolve last year I’ve been traveling and working out simultaneously (RARE). This is something that finally works for me and I truly believe in. All you need is some @pvolve equipment, a small space (can even be a hotel room), a device to stream on and WiFi. node.text: Sneak peek at the magic that’s coming from my shoot with the incredible @emmabassill in @itsherown for @modelistemagazine, adorned in @effyjewelry. It was really fun for me to shoot with such a talented photographer and pretend to be a serious model for a sec (I’m used to shooting primarily with @zackkalter and smiling in almost every photo lol). So excited to see how the photos we shot turn out! @garzablancaloscabos #ModeAroundTheGlobe #garzablancaloscabos #EffyJewelry

node.text: I couldn’t be more ready or excited to announce the inevitable. DRUMROLL PLZ… I have created MY OWN swimwear line! I aptly named it HEROWN, because after years of working on varying levels of design collaborations with brands (and taking notes along the way) this is something I can call my own. It’s also a play on my full name, Helen Ruth Owen. And these past few days I’ve been in Cabo, with some of my best friends, shooting my creations to be featured in @modelistemagazine. PINCH ME. @itsherown is coming! #modearoundtheglobe
